WEBVTT

00:07:28.083 --> 00:07:30.684
In examining another cannabinoid,

00:07:30.708 --> 00:07:32.018
cannabidiol --

00:07:32.042 --> 00:07:33.809
that is, CBD --

00:07:33.833 --> 00:07:36.393
we were actually surprised
to see features relevant

00:07:36.417 --> 00:07:40.000
to alleviating opioid
addiction-related behaviors.

00:07:40.708 --> 00:07:43.958
So there my journey turned to CBD.

00:07:45.875 --> 00:07:49.434
So what's this CBD that has moved
from virtual obscurity

00:07:49.458 --> 00:07:50.726
only a few years ago

00:07:50.750 --> 00:07:52.559
to everywhere in society --

00:07:52.583 --> 00:07:54.018
in your coffee in the morning,

00:07:54.042 --> 00:07:55.518
your water at lunch

00:07:55.542 --> 00:07:57.125
and your beer at dinner?

00:07:58.625 --> 00:08:01.268
CBD comes from the cannabis plant,